44 (b) Addition of the college transfer program shall not decrease an institution's ability to
45 provide programs within its basic mission of vocational and technical training and basic academic
46 education.
47 (c) The State Board of Community Colleges shall develop appropriate criteria and
48 standards to regulate the addition of the college transfer program to institutions.
49 (d) The State Board of Community Colleges shall develop appropriate criteria and
50 standards to regulate the operation of college transfer programs.
