1 (2) A system of supports that would be provided for apprentices, including
2 qualifications of mentor teachers and a schedule of supervision.
3 (3) Alternative sources of funding to support apprenticeships that could be paired
4 with State funds received under the Program, including federal workforce
5 development funds.
6 (4) An explanation of how the unit would incorporate its registered teacher
7 apprenticeship program with its advanced teaching roles program to enhance
