43 hundred dollars ($7,500) per apprentice.
44 2. For each mentor teacher, up to a maximum of five thousand
45 dollars ($5,000) per mentor teacher.
46 b. An apprenticeship employer may provide a salary supplement for any
47 other teacher employed by the local school administrative unit who
48 agrees to become the teacher of record for additional students to
49 facilitate the operation of the registered apprenticeship program in that
50 unit, up to a maximum of three thousand dollars ($3,000).
