1 Each local board of education shall provide instruction on social media and its effects on
2 health, including social, emotional, and physical effects. Instruction shall be provided once
3 during elementary school, once during middle school, and twice during high school. Instruction
4 may be included as part of the mental and emotional health instruction provided pursuant to
5 G.S. 115C-81.25. Instruction on this topic shall include at least the following:
6 (1) Negative effects of social media on mental health, including addiction.
