8 (3) Methods of manipulating behavior using social media.
9 (4) The permanency of information shared online.
10 (5) How to maintain personal security.
11 (6) How to identify cyberbullying, predatory behavior, and human trafficking on
12 the internet.
13 (7) How to report suspicious behavior encountered on the internet.
14 (8) Personal and interpersonal skills or character education that enhances
15 individual level protective factors and mitigates or reduces risk-taking or
16 harmful behavior."
