41 SECTION 7.46. Notwithstanding G.S. 115C-83.12, 115C-150.12C(3a),
42 115C-218.85(5), 115C-269.20(a)(2), or 116-239.8, of the funds appropriated to the Department
43 of Public Instruction, one million two hundred thousand dollars ($1,200,000) in nonrecurring
44 funds for the 2025-2026 fiscal year shall be used to contract with JFL Enterprises, Inc., for a
