36 of Commission employment, duties, or responsibilities, or that such person
37 had a reasonable basis for believing occurred within the scope of Commission
38 employment, duties, or responsibilities, provided that the actual or alleged act,
39 error, or omission did not result from the intentional or willful or wanton
40 misconduct of that person.
