45 Member State's state action immunity or state action affirmative defense with
46 respect to antitrust claims under the Sherman Act, Clayton Act, or any other
47 state or federal antitrust or anticompetitive law or regulation.
48 (6) Nothing in this Compact shall be construed to be a waiver of sovereign
49 immunity by the Member States or by the Commission.
