23 of students. The admission criteria may give priority to students with no parent that has completed
24 a two- or four-year degree and shall include the following:
25 (1) Demonstrated academic achievement.
26 (2) Demonstrated student interest in attendance.
27 (3) Documented parental support for student attendance.
