29 updated phone number exists, the school shall have the phrases "To reach the Suicide and Crisis
30 Lifeline, call 988 or text HOME to 741741" and "To reach the NC Peer Warmline, call
31 855-733-7762" in the following places:
32 (1) On any new student identification (student ID) issued to a student in grades
33 six through 12. The text shall be in a conspicuous location on the student ID.
34 The text may be printed on the ID or affixed by sticker. Nothing in this section
35 requires a school to issue a student ID.
36 (2) On the school website.
37 (3) On the home screen of any electronic device issued to students.
38 (4) On any school agenda or calendar, whether digital or printed.
39 (5) On a document during any suicide awareness activity.
40 (6) On a document when the student registers to attend the school."
