1 1. Is in the top twenty-five percent (25%) of teachers in the
2 teacher's respective local school administrative unit according
3 to the EVAAS student growth index score for third grade
4 reading from the previous school year.
5 2. Is in the top twenty-five percent (25%) of teachers in the
6 teacher's respective local school administrative unit according
7 to the EVAAS student growth index score for fourth or fifth
8 grade reading from the previous school year.
9 3. Is in the top twenty-five percent (25%) of teachers in the
