41 mixed beverage tax receipts available in Budget Code 14460, Budget Fund 134603 for transfer
42 to Budget Code 24410 to implement the replacement project for outdated data systems developed
43 pursuant to this section. Beginning in the fiscal year following project completion, the
44 DMH/DD/SUS may use up to one million two hundred thousand dollars ($1,200,000) of mixed
45 beverage tax receipts each fiscal year to cover operations and maintenance costs for the
46 replacement system.
