24 SECTION 12.2.(g) G.S. 159G-20 reads as rewritten:
25 "§ 159G-20. Definitions.
26 The following definitions apply in this Chapter:
27 …
28 (21) Targeted interest rate project. – Either Any of the following types of projects:
