26 2017-10 is repealed. Section 13.9 of S.L. 2000-67 is codified within Part 8E, as follows:
27 (1) Section 13.9(a) is codified as G.S. 143-215.73N, to be entitled "Findings."
28 (2) Sections 13.9(b), 13.9(c), and 13.9(d) are codified as subsections (a), (b), and
29 (c) of G.S. 143-215.73O, to be entitled "Beach and inlet management plan."
