42 (3) Upon raising an additional sum of three million dollars ($3,000,000) in
43 non-State funding for a total amount of seven million dollars ($7,000,000) in
44 non-State funds, the North Carolina Symphony shall receive the final sum of
45 seven hundred thousand dollars ($700,000) in the 2026-2027 fiscal year.
