19 misbranding of food, drugs, cosmetics, etc., with the intent to cause serious
20 injury in violation of G.S. 14-34.4.
21 (6) Any felony offense involving human trafficking of an adult, including any
22 violation of G.S. 14-43.11 (Human trafficking), G.S. 14-43.12 (Involuntary
23 servitude), or G.S. 14-43.13 (Sexual servitude).
24 …."
25 SECTION 19.4.(b) This section becomes effective December 1, 2025, and applies
