36 SECTION 31A.5.(a) The Office of State Human Resources shall submit to the State
37 Human Resources Commission, the Joint Legislative Oversight Committee on General
38 Government, and the Governor an improved process for performance management and
39 evaluation. The State Human Resources Commission, subject to the approval of the Governor,
40 shall adopt a new performance management and evaluation policy by March 15, 2026.
41 SECTION 31A.5.(b) This section is effective when it becomes law.
