7 Veterans' Affairs Commission Department is not required to select or recommend the vendor
8 offering the lowest cost proposal but shall select or recommend the vendor who, in the opinion
9 of the Commission, Department, offers the proposal most advantageous to the veterans and the
10 State of North Carolina.
