37 SECTION 36.5. Of the funds appropriated in this act to the Department of Revenue,
38 the sum of four million four hundred thousand dollars ($4,400,000) in recurring funds for each
39 fiscal year of the 2025-2027 fiscal biennium shall be used to continue and expand the
40 Department's tax fraud analysis contract through the Government Data Analytics Center
41 (GDAC). These funds shall be used in each fiscal year to fund detection analytics, software,
42 information reporting, collections case management, collections optimization, managed services,
43 and technical infrastructure. The Department of Revenue shall continue to coordinate with the
44 GDAC and utilize the subject matter expertise and technical infrastructure available through
45 existing GDAC public-private partnerships for fraud detection and analytics infrastructure.
