19 PREVENTING IDENTITY FRAUD AND ABUSE
20 SECTION 40.8. In order to prevent identity fraud and abuse, State agencies shall
21 ensure that all State benefits and entitlement programs responsible for the distribution of funds
22 to individuals implement and use authentication and identity-proofing systems prior to any
23 disbursement of funds. To the greatest extent feasible, such systems shall comply with National
24 Institute of Standards and Technology (NIST) Authenticator Assurance Level 2 and Identity
25 Assurance Level 2 requirements.
