19 "§ 58-86-41. Amount due for membership; payments credited to separate member
20 accounts.
21 (a) Unless otherwise provided under this Article, each member of the Pension Fund shall
22 pay the sum of fifteen dollars ($15.00) per month to the Pension Fund for membership in the
23 fund for a period not to exceed 20 years.
