12 WORK ZONE DYNAMIC SPEED DISPLAY SIGNS
13 SECTION 43.23. Of the funds appropriated from the Highway Fund to the
14 Department of Transportation in this act, one million dollars ($1,000,000) shall be used to
15 purchase dynamic speed display signs and implement their use in highway work zones. For
